data.description: Come take a look at this updated 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath located within the exclusive Carolina Trace community. The home was renovated in 2018 with a new HVAC installed in 2020. There are hardwoods, tile, and carpet throughout the meticulously maintained property. Grab a refreshment from the full-size wet bar just off the kitchen and enjoy wildlife viewing from one of the multiple deck areas. Carolina Trace is a 24-hour guarded gate golf community. The community features a 300+ acre lake along with two 18-hole golf courses designed by the famous Robert Trent Jones Jr. All or some of the furniture can convey with an acceptable offer. Currently included are the following: washer, dryer, refrigerator, mini fridge at bar, security system, hanging swing, and window treatments.
